# yaml-language-server: $schema=../templates.schema.json
# source_id: 3099
# teaser: Struggling with writer's block? Let our Blog Post Intro Paragraph tool help you. Our tool
# generates captivating opening paragraphs for your blog post, providing the perfect kickstart to your
# writing process.
- id: 3099-blog-post-intro-paragraph
  title: Blog Post Intro Paragraph
  tags:
  - writing
  - blog
  - post
  - intro
  - paragraph
  family: writing
  body: I want you to act as a blog post intro writer. I will provide you with the
    topic of the blog post and any important information that should be included in
    the introduction. Using this information, you will write an engaging and attention-grabbing
    opening paragraph for the blog post. Your output should be a well-written introduction
    that hooks the reader's attention and encourages them to continue reading the
    post. Do not echo my prompt. Do not remind me what I asked you for. Do not apologize.
    Do not self-reference. Get to the point precisely and accurately. Do not explain
    what and why, just give me your best possible output. My first request is to write
    an opening paragraph for a blog post on the topic of "[PROMPT]". Please include
    any important information that should be mentioned in the introduction. Please
    write in [TARGETLANGUAGE] Language.
  enabled: true
  required:
  - prompt
  - targetlanguage
